parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cracking of Cowling Section in Ford Bus Chassis
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the cowling section where body brackets are mounted to the frame can lead to a structural failure, causing the body to drop on the frame, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: body brackets mounted to the frame are compromised
potential for body to drop on frame.
